title: Former JCSU basketball coach Bob Moore, 73, dies
text:
Published By: Charlotte Observer: Sports - Today 
Former Johnson C. Smith and Virginia Union basketball coach Bob Moore has diedMoore, who was 73, was 148-101 with J.C. Smith from 1978 to 19...
